    },
    {
      "segments": [
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:1.1",
          "pli": "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā rājagahe viharati gijjhakūṭe pabbate acirapakkante devadatte. ",
          "en": "At one time the Buddha was staying near Rājagaha, on the Vulture’s Peak Mountain, not long after Devadatta had left. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:1.2",
          "pli": "Tatra bhagavā devadattaṃ ārabbha bhikkhū āmantesi: ",
          "en": "There the Buddha spoke to the mendicants about Devadatta: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:1.3",
          "pli": "“sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kālena kālaṃ attavipattiṃ paccavekkhitā hoti. ",
          "en": "“Mendicants, it’s good for a mendicant to check their own failings from time to time. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:1.4",
          "pli": "Sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kālena kālaṃ paravipattiṃ paccavekkhitā hoti. ",
          "en": "It’s good for a mendicant to check the failings of others from time to time. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:1.5",
          "pli": "Sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kālena kālaṃ attasampattiṃ paccavekkhitā hoti. ",
          "en": "It’s good for a mendicant to check their own successes from time to time. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:1.6",
          "pli": "Sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu kālena kālaṃ parasampattiṃ paccavekkhitā hoti. ",
          "en": "It’s good for a mendicant to check the successes of others from time to time. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:1.7",
          "pli": "Aṭṭhahi, bhikkhave, asaddhammehi abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto devadatto āpāyiko nerayiko kappaṭṭho atekiccho. ",
          "en": "Overcome and overwhelmed by eight things that oppose the true teaching, Devadatta is going to a place of loss, to hell, there to remain for an eon, irredeemable. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.1",
          "pli": "Katamehi aṭṭhahi? ",
          "en": "What eight? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.2",
          "pli": "Lābhena hi, bhikkhave, abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto devadatto āpāyiko nerayiko kappaṭṭho atekiccho. ",
          "en": "Overcome and overwhelmed by gain … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.3",
          "pli": "Alābhena, bhikkhave … pe … ",
          "en": "loss … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.4",
          "pli": "yasena, bhikkhave … ",
          "en": "fame … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.5",
          "pli": "ayasena, bhikkhave … ",
          "en": "disgrace … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.6",
          "pli": "sakkārena, bhikkhave … ",
          "en": "honor … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.7",
          "pli": "asakkārena, bhikkhave … ",
          "en": "dishonor … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.8",
          "pli": "pāpicchatāya, bhikkhave … ",
          "en": "wicked desires … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.9",
          "pli": "pāpamittatāya, bhikkhave, abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto devadatto āpāyiko nerayiko kappaṭṭho atekiccho. ",
          "en": "bad friendship, Devadatta is going to a place of loss, to hell, there to remain for an eon, irredeemable. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:2.10",
          "pli": "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, aṭṭhahi asaddhammehi abhibhūto pariyādinnacitto devadatto āpāyiko nerayiko kappaṭṭho atekiccho. ",
          "en": "Overcome and overwhelmed by these eight things that oppose the true teaching, Devadatta is going to a place of loss, to hell, there to remain for an eon, irredeemable. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:3.1",
          "pli": "Sādhu, bhikkhave, bhikkhu uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya, ",
          "en": "It’s good for a mendicant, whenever they encounter it, to overcome gain … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:3.2",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": "loss … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:3.3",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ yasaṃ … ",
          "en": "fame … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:3.4",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ … ",
          "en": "disgrace … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:3.5",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": "honor … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:3.6",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": "dishonor … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:3.7",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ … ",
          "en": "wicked desires … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:3.8",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya. ",
          "en": "bad friendship. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:4.1",
          "pli": "Kiñca, bhikkhave, bhikkhu atthavasaṃ paṭicca uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya, ",
          "en": "What advantage does a mendicant gain by overcoming these eight things? "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:4.2",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:4.3",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ yasaṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:4.4",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:4.5",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:4.6",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:4.7",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:4.8",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya? ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.1",
          "pli": "Yaṃ hissa, bhikkhave, uppannaṃ lābhaṃ anabhibhuyya viharato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya viharato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. ",
          "en": "The distressing and feverish defilements that might arise in someone who lives without overcoming these eight things do not arise when they have overcome them. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.2",
          "pli": "Yaṃ hissa, bhikkhave, uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.3",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ yasaṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.4",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.5",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.6",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.7",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.8",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ anabhibhuyya viharato uppajjeyyuṃ āsavā vighātapariḷāhā, uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya viharato evaṃsa te āsavā vighātapariḷāhā na honti. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.9",
          "pli": "Idaṃ kho, bhikkhave, bhikkhu atthavasaṃ paṭicca uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya, ",
          "en": "This is the advantage that a mendicant gains by overcoming these eight things. "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.10",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.11",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ yasaṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.12",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.13",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.14",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.15",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ … ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:5.16",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya vihareyya. ",
          "en": " "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.1",
          "pli": "Tasmātiha, bhikkhave, evaṃ sikkhitabbaṃ: ",
          "en": "So, mendicants, you should train like this: "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.2",
          "pli": "‘uppannaṃ lābhaṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya viharissāma, ",
          "en": "‘Whenever we encounter it, we will overcome gain … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.3",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ alābhaṃ … pe … ",
          "en": "loss … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.4",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ yasaṃ … ",
          "en": "fame … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.5",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ ayasaṃ … ",
          "en": "disgrace … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.6",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ sakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": "honor … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.7",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ asakkāraṃ … ",
          "en": "dishonor … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.8",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpicchataṃ … ",
          "en": "wicked desires … "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.9",
          "pli": "uppannaṃ pāpamittataṃ abhibhuyya abhibhuyya viharissāmā’ti. ",
          "en": "bad friendship.’ "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.10",
          "pli": "Evañhi vo, bhikkhave, sikkhitabban”ti. ",
          "en": "That’s how you should train.” "
        },
        {
          "scid": "an8.7:6.11",
          "pli": "Sattamaṃ. ",
          "en": ""
        }
      ],
